{"tid":2318554,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"factcheck lab: 網傳CNN轉風向指侵或勝算，實為九月節目","createTime":"2020-12-09T11:52:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-09T11:52:52.000Z","uid":13505,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fcef8f1b34ed50f1dec22c5b1820ff5af7de0e4c","tid":2318554,"uid":13505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T11:52:52.000Z","msg":"【注意消息來源及影片發佈日期】<br />\n<br />\n自11月28日起，網絡流傳消息指美國電視台《CNN》「轉風向」，承認特朗普可能連任。<br />\n<br />\n經查證，有關消息引述的《CNN》節目影片實際上在9月27日播出，為分析及評論內容，主持當時探討假如特朗普在大選中落敗，共和黨如何在合憲的情況下讓他連任。<br />\n<br />\n節目本身在大選前播出，不可能是《CNN》改變「拜登當選」報導的證據，因此「《CNN》轉風向」的說法錯誤。<br />\n<br />\n完整查核報告見 <a href=\"http://factchecklab.org/20201209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffactchecklab.org%2F20201209&d=zhjqHwqbwmwTWRz%2FWGYaUILj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=e21a7516\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">factchecklab.org/20201209</a><br />\n<br />\n----------<br />\nFacebook 👉 <a href=\"http://fb.me/factchecklabhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.me%2Ffactchecklabhk&d=zhjqHwqbwmwTWRz%2FWGYaUILj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=113ba69c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">fb.me/factchecklabhk</a><br />\nTelegram 👉 <a href=\"http://t.me/factchecklab\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffactchecklab&d=zhjqHwqbwmwTWRz%2FWGYaUILj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=e0701143\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/factchecklab</a><br />\nInstagram 👉 <a href=\"http://instagram.com/factchecklab\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Ffactchecklab&d=zhjqHwqbwmwTWRz%2FWGYaUILj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=df4753b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">instagram.com/factchecklab</a><br />\nTwitter 👉 <a href=\"http://twitter.com/factchecklab\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffactchecklab&d=zhjqHwqbwmwTWRz%2FWGYaUILj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=8183d532\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">twitter.com/factchecklab</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/103495551396318/posts/201930821552790/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F103495551396318%2Fposts%2F201930821552790%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=zhjqHwqbwmwTWRz%2FWGYaUILj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=dcbbf586\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/103495551396318/posts/201930821552790/?d=n</a>"}]}